articles.title: Biden sending some troops to Eastern Europe to deter Russia from invading Ukraine - New York Post
articles.description: President Biden said Friday that he’s sending US troops — but “not too many” — to Eastern Europe amid concern about a potential Russian invasion of Ukraine.

articles.title: President Joe Biden to deploy US troops 'in the near term' as Pentagon warns of Putin's full range of military options in Ukraine - ABC News
